ZH: 他独自一人去了电影院。
EN: He went to the cinema alone.

ZH: 她独自一人在家度过了整个周末。
EN: She spent the whole weekend alone at home.

ZH: 孩子们独自在公园玩耍。
EN: The children played alone in the park.

ZH: 他独自一人承担了这个任务。
EN: He took on the task alone.

ZH: 她独自驾车去了北方旅行。
EN: She traveled alone to the north by car.

ZH: 我独自一个人说话感觉很奇怪。
EN: It feels strange to talk to myself alone.

ZH: 他独自一人站在山顶欣赏美丽的风景。
EN: He stood alone at the mountaintop, enjoying the beautiful scenery.

ZH: 她独自在海滩漫步，享受宁静。
EN: She strolled alone on the beach, enjoying the tranquility.

ZH: 他喜欢独自思考问题。
EN: He likes to contemplate problems alone.

ZH: 婴儿独自在房间里哭泣。
EN: The baby cries alone in the room.

ZH: 她独自一人走进了陌生的城市。
EN: She entered the unfamiliar city alone.

ZH: 他拒绝了其他人的帮助，坚持独自完成工作。
EN: He refused help from others and insisted on completing the work alone.

ZH: 她独自一人经营着自己的小公司。
EN: She runs her own small company alone.

ZH: 爷爷独自在农田里劳作。
EN: Grandpa works alone in the fields.

ZH: 我喜欢独自坐在咖啡馆里阅读。
EN: I enjoy sitting alone in a coffee shop and reading.

ZH: 他每天独自在音乐室里练习钢琴。
EN: He practices piano alone in the music room every day.

ZH: 那只狗独自躺在阳光下晒太阳。
EN: The dog lies alone in the sun.

ZH: 她独自学会了修自行车。
EN: She learned to fix bicycles alone.

ZH: 我喜欢独自旅行，没有任何依赖。
EN: I enjoy traveling alone, without any dependencies.

ZH: 他独自一人面对困难，努力克服。
EN: He faces difficulties alone and works hard to overcome them.
